Description: Code Analysis Server (casmgr) — MCP server with PostgreSQL in Docker
 Installs the code-analysis MCP daemon as a systemd service (casmgr-server)
 and manages a version-locked PostgreSQL/pgvector container (casmgr-postgres).
 .
 Configuration: /etc/casmgr/config.json
 Data and secrets: /var/casmgr
 Logs: /var/log/casmgr
 .
 The Debian package version matches the Docker Hub tag for casmgr-postgres
 (see /usr/share/casmgr/docker-image after install).
